      *------*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           US     10
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WUSER   9
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WUSME  15
     C                     CALL 'APLR00'
     C                     PARM           US
     C                     PARM           WUSME
     C                     MOVELWUSME     WUSER
      *-----*
      * KEY *
      *-----*
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           IODER
     C                     KFLD           IITEM
